Maxima's glare turned from Hevn to Sideways. "You assume to much, Sideways. 
Last I remembered," she grinned. "I thought you were an Autobot?" Pausing a 
moment. "As well as I am by no means a young-bot. I've been functioning since the 
Golden Age." She was rather proud of that, though, it was painful at times. 

"Now, are you all going to flap your traps? Or will you all allow me to 
Welcome our Decepticon guests?!" 

--part1_1d6.a878596.2c083350_boundary
